<div class="media-wrapper"><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.macstories.net/img_0471-1764686075934.PNG" alt=""><p class="image-caption"></p></div>
<p id="p2">Apple Music has released its annual Apple Music Replay overview of subscribers&rsquo; listening statistics for 2025 along with top charts for 2025. The recap can be accessed on&nbsp;<a href="https://replay.music.apple.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://replay.music.apple.com</a>, where you&rsquo;ll find details about the music you listened to throughout the year, including your top albums, songs, artists, playlists, and genres.</p>
<div class="media-wrapper"><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.macstories.net/img_0473-2-1764686076708.PNG" alt="Replay includes statistics about your listening habits."><p class="image-caption">Replay includes statistics about your listening habits.</p></div>
<p id="p4">As with past years, Replay &lsquo;25 begins with an animated highlights reel of your year in music set to the songs you enjoyed throughout the year. Replay also spotlights listening milestones like the total number of minutes listened and the number of artists and songs played. Subscribers can browse through their statistics by month, too. Your Replay &lsquo;25 playlist, which includes your 100 most listened-to songs is available from the Replay website and Apple&rsquo;s Music app. In addition to Replay &lsquo;25 Apple Music released top charts for countries around the world and genres.</p>
<div class="media-wrapper"><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.macstories.net/cleanshot-2025-12-02-at-09-35-26-2x-1764686192747.png" alt="Apple Music's top charts."><p class="image-caption">Apple Music&rsquo;s top charts.</p></div>
<p id="p6">The timing of Replay &lsquo;25 is opportune for me, since Federico and I are beginning to assemble our lists of favorite music of 2025 for an upcoming episode of&nbsp;<a href="https://www.macstories.net/unwind/" rel="noopener noreferrer">MacStories Unwind</a>. Most of all though, I just enjoy using Replay &lsquo;25 as a way to revisit my favorite music of the year.</p>
<p id="p7">To view your own Replay 2025 statistics, visit&nbsp;<a href="https://replay.music.apple.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">music.apple.com/replay</a>.</p>
